This is an HKMU official mobile app dedicated for alumni through which they can enjoy one-stop alumni services in a more convenient way.

Major features include:
•	Alumni e-card – Identity proof of HKMU alumni;
•	HKMU Alumni Association – Register as member through the app to enjoy exclusive member privileges;
•	Happenings – Keep abreast of development and updates of HKMU;
•	University publications – Read Alumni Linkage and MU Connect anytime; 



and many more. Download the app and register now!
